RVC/AIR\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|1980\n|''Come Along''\n|align=\"center\"|32\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|1984\n|''Come Along II''\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|\n|-\n|1985\n|''Tatsuro Collection''\n|align=\"center\"|35\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|1986\n|''Ballad for You''\n|align=\"center\"|37\n|\n|-\n|''Rock'n Funk Tatsu''\n|align=\"center\"|59\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|1990\n|''Best Pack I (1976\u20131979)''\n|align=\"center\"|\u2014\n|\n|-\n|''Best Pack II (1979\u20131982)''\n|align=\"center\"|\u2014\n|\n|-\n|1995\n|''[[Treasures (Tatsuro Yamashita album)|Treasures]]''\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|align=\"center\"|[[East West Records|Moon/East West]]\n|\n|-\n|2002\n|''[[Rarities (Tatsuro Yamashita album)|Rarities]]''\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|rowspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"|Moon/Warner\n|\n|-\n|2012\n|''[[Opus (All Time Best 1975-2012)]]''\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|<ref name=\"hmv\">{{cite news |last1=\u7530\u4ee3 |first1=\u8cb4\u4e4b |title=HMV\u30a4\u30f3\u30bf\u30d3\u30e5\u30fc\u3011 \u5c71\u4e0b\u9054\u90ce \u300eOPUS \uff5eALL TIME BEST 1975-2012\uff5e\u300f Facebook |url=https://www.hmv.co.jp/news/article/1208200027/ |accessdate=22 November 2019 |publisher=HMV |date=14 September 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n|2017\n|''Come Along III''\n|align=\"center\"|\u2014\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Other releases ===\nFollowing materials are not marketed to the record retailers, though they have been available via mail order to his official [[fan club]].<ref name=\"fanclub\">{{cite web |url=http://www.tatsuro.co.jp/fan/ |title=\u5c71\u4e0b\u9054\u90ce OFFICIAL WEB SITE: \u30d5\u30a1\u30f3\u30af\u30e9\u30d6\u901a\u8ca9CD |website=tatsuro.co.jp |language=ja |accessdate=2015-07-30}}</ref>\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Album\n!Label\n!Footnotes\n|-\n|''Add Some Music to Your Day''\n|rowspan=\"4\" align=\"center\"|Wild Honey\n|\n* [[Cover album]] that Yamashita and his friends produced and released independently in 1972\n|-\n|''The Works of Tatsuro Yamashita Vol.1''\n|\n* Compilation comprises his compositions written for other artists\n|-\n|''Tatsuro Yamashita CM Collection Vol.1''\n|rowspan=\"2\"|\n* Compilation comprises materials originally used in the advertisements and never issued on his official releases\n|-\n|''Tatsuro Yamashita CM Collection Vol.2''\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Singles ===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!A-Side\n!B-Side(s) / Double A-Side<br /><ref name=\"singlediscography1\">{{cite web |url=http://www.tatsuro.co.jp/disco/single_01.html |title=\u5c71\u4e0b\u9054\u90ce OFFICIAL WEBSITE {{pipe}} DISCOGRAPHY {{pipe}} SINGLE Part 1 |website=tatsuro.co.jp |language=ja |accessdate=2015-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720201434/http://www.tatsuro.co.jp/disco/single_01.html |archive-date=2015-07-20 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"singlediscography2\">{{cite web |url=http://www.tatsuro.co.jp/disco/single_02.html |title=\u5c71\u4e0b\u9054\u90ce OFFICIAL WEBSITE {{pipe}} DISCOGRAPHY {{pipe}} SINGLE Part 2 |website=tatsuro.co.jp |language=ja |accessdate=2015-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801110534/http://www.tatsuro.co.jp/disco/single_02.html |archive-date=2015-08-01 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"singlediscography3\">{{cite web |url=http://www.tatsuro.co.jp/disco/single_03.html |title=\u5c71\u4e0b\u9054\u90ce OFFICIAL WEBSITE {{pipe}} DISCOGRAPHY {{pipe}} SINGLE Part 3 |website=tatsuro.co.jp |language=ja |accessdate=2015-07-29}}</ref>\n\n!Chart positions<br />([[Oricon|JP]])<ref name=\"oricon single\">{{cite web | url=http://www7a.biglobe.ne.jp/~yamag/single/yamasita.html|website=Yamachan Land (Japan's charts archives)  - Singles Chart Daijiten - | title=Tatsuro Yamashita | language=Japanese | accessdate=2009-07-01 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20071016164223/http://www7a.biglobe.ne.jp/~yamag/single/yamasita.html | archivedate=2007-10-16 }}</ref><ref name=\"oriconartistsinglesonline\">{{cite web |url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/212703/products/single/ |